==Ladino==


'''abásho'''

# [[Below]].

===Etymology===
Old Spanish ''[[abaxo]],'' from the Latin ''[[ad]]+[[bassus]].''

====Phrases====
'''abashár abásho'''

# To go down.

'''los de abásho'''

# The departed, the dead.

'''tódo sta de arríva abásho'''

# Everything is upside down.

